            <title>[HIVE-27113] Increasing default for hive.thrift.client.max.message.size to 2 GB</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-27113</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
HIVE_THRIFT_CLIENT_MAX_MESSAGE_SIZE(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hive.thrift.client.max.message.size&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;1gb&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; SizeValidator(-1L, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, (&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Integer&lt;/span&gt;.MAX_VALUE, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;),
&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Thrift client configuration &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; max message size. 0 or -1 will use the &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; defined in the Thrift &quot;&lt;/span&gt; +
&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;library. The upper limit is 2147483648 bytes (or 2gb).&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&#160;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Documentation on the help suggests setting 2147483648 while Integer Max is 2147483647. So, it actually becomes -1 and gets set to thrift default limit (100 MB)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
